Class Project

java.lang.Object
  org.pimslims.business.XtalObject
      org.pimslims.business.core.model.Project

public class Project
    
extends XtalObject





Details about a project


A project is a a group of samples belonging to a group


Each project will have an owner and a localcontact (for projects that are
outside the lab where the experimentation is being done, a local contact is
needed to manage the samples in-house)
